::: {#edu-exp}
I am currently a PhD student in Economics at [IRES](https://uclouvain.be/en/research-institutes/lidam/ires) (UCLouvain) and a teaching assistant at [FOPES](https://uclouvain.be/fr/facultes/espo/fopes) (UCLouvain). My research focuses on the economics of inequalities: I am currently working on quantifying the evolution of income inequalities in Belgium, using [Distributional National Accounts](https://wid.world/fr/news-article/2020-distributional-national-accounts-guidelines-dina-2/). I also teach a course at the [Haute École ISFSC](https://www.isfsc.be/) in Brussels.
:::

